<br>It is a tool to balance supply and demand on GB's Network and manage operational issues in real time
<br>Continuous open online auction
<br>Trading period : 30  minutes
<br>Auction gate 60-90 min before real time
<br>Can submit <a data-href="202406101512a - Bids and offers" href="docs\202406101512a-bids-and-offers.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">202406101512a - Bids and offers</a>
<br>Decision:

