 <br>
<br>Instruction to the participants that ENCC (<a rel="noopener" class="external-link" href="https://www.nationalgrideso.com/who-we-are/electricity-national-control-centre" target="_blank">https://www.nationalgrideso.com/who-we-are/electricity-national-control-centre</a>) wants to change their output.
<br>Participants have to accept these BOAs - Participant agree to act on these instruction, hence looks like non binding
<br>Source: <a rel="noopener" class="external-link" href="https://www.nationalgrideso.com/what-we-do/electricity-national-control-centre/what-balancing-mechanism#:~:text=Once%20we%20accept,system%20in%20balance" target="_blank">https://www.nationalgrideso.com/what-we-do/electricity-national-control-centre/what-balancing-mechanism#:~:text=Once%20we%20accept,system%20in%20balance</a>]]></description><link>docs\202406101512b-bid-offer-acceptance-(boas).html</link><guid isPermaLink="false">docs/202406101512b - Bid Offer Acceptance (BOAs).md</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Prabhat Ranjan]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 08:02:20 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[202406101512c - Action and pricing]]></title><description><![CDATA[<a class="tag" href="?query=tag:Balancing_market" style="background-color: rgb(4, 108, 116); color: white; font-weight: 700; border: none; border-radius: 1em; padding: 0.2em 0.5em;">#Balancing_market</a> <a class="tag" href="?query=tag:UK" style="background-color: rgb(4, 108, 116); color: white; font-weight: 700; border: none; border-radius: 1em; padding: 0.2em 0.5em;">#UK</a> 
 <br><a href=".?query=tag:Balancing_market" class="tag" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#Balancing_market</a> <a href=".?query=tag:UK" class="tag" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#UK</a><br>
BM actions are broadly of two categories:<br>
<br>
Energy - These actions are to manage supply and demand imbalances (energy related ancillary service)

<br>Price of marginal action determine the <a data-href="Energy imbalance price" href="Energy imbalance price" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">Energy imbalance price</a> for each <a data-href="settlement period" href="settlement period" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">settlement period</a> (pay-as-cleared)


<br>
System - These actions are mostly for management of system, such as constraints, stability and voltage. They are procured via same <a data-href="202406101512b - Bid Offer Acceptance (BOAs)" href="docs\202406101512b-bid-offer-acceptance-(boas).html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">202406101512b - Bid Offer Acceptance (BOAs)</a>, but tagged separately to to not affect <a data-href="Energy imbalance price" href="Energy imbalance price" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener">Energy imbalance price</a>

<br>Source:<br>
<a data-tooltip-position="top" aria-label="https://www.nationalgrideso.com/document/304131/download" rel="noopener" class="external-link" href="https://www.nationalgrideso.com/document/304131/download" target="_blank">download (nationalgrideso.com)</a> pg. 35]]></description><link>docs\202406101512c-action-and-pricing.html</link><guid isPermaLink="false">docs/202406101512c - Action and pricing.md</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Prabhat Ranjan]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:27:56 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[202406101532 - Balancing services in UK - overview]]></title><description><![CDATA[<a class="tag" href="?query=tag:Balancing_market" style="background-color: rgb(4, 108, 116); color: white; font-weight: 700; border: none; border-radius: 1em; padding: 0.2em 0.5em;">#Balancing_market</a> <a class="tag" href="?query=tag:UK" style="background-color: rgb(4, 108, 116); color: white; font-weight: 700; border: none; border-radius: 1em; padding: 0.2em 0.5em;">#UK</a> 
